  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/134782ec167323dd335c6e079ddd45a5.poster.avif?t=1676315354\" width=610 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/134782ec167323dd335c6e079ddd45a5.webm?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/134782ec167323dd335c6e079ddd45a5.mp4?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Logic Light is a 2D minimalist puzzle adventure game in which you must restore the electricity of the houses after a blackout, advancing through the levels by repairing circuits using your tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/6d46f6a86bb8de46622ecc9208cbdc2b.poster.avif?t=1676315354\" width=610 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/6d46f6a86bb8de46622ecc9208cbdc2b.webm?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/6d46f6a86bb8de46622ecc9208cbdc2b.mp4?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Drag available energy sources and tools onto the terrain and watch the energy flow, lighting up the town's houses or lighting points and advance to the next level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/257b7312edb7f292d03166a04d7995c8.poster.avif?t=1676315354\" width=610 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/257b7312edb7f292d03166a04d7995c8.webm?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712950/extras/257b7312edb7f292d03166a04d7995c8.mp4?t=1676315354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 80 Levels<br></li><li> Lo-fi Music</li></ul>",
